buse and to submit a report to Congress on the results of such study not later than "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1993-10-01"},"text":"Oct. 1, 1993","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
